{"ID":"20250404131424-lsuwjdx","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250404131424-lsuwjdx","title":"FreeRTOS","type":"doc","updated":"20250404172416"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250404131424-7w3s8py","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20250404131424-7w3s8py","updated":"20250404172416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需要理解的简单汇编指令"}]},{"ID":"20250404171812-2oj2x0m","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250404171812-2oj2x0m","updated":"20250404171904"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"1.读内存\nLDR R0, [R1, #4];读地址\"R1+4\"，得到的4字节数据存入R0\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250404171905-f4wjs92","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250404171905-f4wjs92","updated":"20250404172046"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"2.写内存\nSTR R0, [R1, #4];把R0的4字节数据写入地址\"R1+4\"\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250404172047-4d9ecvi","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250404172047-4d9ecvi","updated":"20250404172234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"3.加减\nADD R0, R1, R2; R0 = R1 + R2\nADD R0, R0, #1; R0 = R0 + 1\nSUB R0, R1, R2; R0 = R1 - R2\nSUB R0, R0, #1; R0 = R0 - 1\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250404172127-cfsa1q0","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250404172127-cfsa1q0","updated":"20250404172307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"4.比较\nCMP R0, R1;结果保存在PSR(程序状态寄存器)\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250404172308-tjwqlwh","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20250404172308-tjwqlwh","updated":"20250404172414"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dW5kZWZpbmVk"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"5.跳转\nB main; Branch，直接跳转\nBL main; Branch and Link，先把返回地址保存在LR寄存器里再跳转\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20250404172416-00rfa95","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250404172416-00rfa95","updated":"20250404172416"}}]}